SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Concerning Prescription Drugs (Repeal of Schedule F to the Food and Drug Regulations)
PrecisRegulations amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS CONCERNING PRESCRIPTION DRUGS (REPEAL OF SCHEDULE F TO THE FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS) in order to bring greater efficiency to the process of adding or removing drugs from a schedule maintained in regulations without compromising the well-established scientific review and consultation process.
